cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the security and privacy of personal information in the context of Internet services. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.SE (Software Engineering), as the paper also touches upon user behavior and software design.
